WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:01:17.600 --> 00:01:23.720
Today we are celebrating the resurrection of Christ.

00:01:24.120 --> 00:01:27.360
With it we have to also celebrate

00:01:27.760 --> 00:01:30.800
the resurrection of human beings,

00:01:31.040 --> 00:01:33.240
of Sahaja Yogis

00:01:33.520 --> 00:01:39.120
who have been resurrected as realised souls.

00:01:39.920 --> 00:01:43.720
With that we have to understand

00:01:44.120 --> 00:01:48.840
that we enter into a new awareness.

00:01:49.120 --> 00:01:51.400
There was no need for Christ

00:01:51.640 --> 00:01:54.080
to enter into any new awareness,

00:01:54.120 --> 00:01:56.120
He had to come down

00:01:56.120 --> 00:02:00.000
and again to show to this world

00:02:00.280 --> 00:02:05.760
that you are the eternal life,

00:02:05.920 --> 00:02:11.120
that you lead a life

00:02:12.320 --> 00:02:16.440
that is spiritual, which never perishes.

00:02:16.880 --> 00:02:21.200
You have to rise into that new realm

00:02:21.920 --> 00:02:26.920
which is the realm

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:30.160
of God Almighty,

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:34.120
what you call the Kingdom of God.

00:02:34.280 --> 00:02:37.960
And He said it very clearly

00:02:38.160 --> 00:02:40.280
to Nicodemus

00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:43.800
that "You have to be born again,"

00:02:44.880 --> 00:02:47.640
and when he asked

00:02:47.920 --> 00:02:51.280
"Am I to enter back into my mother's womb to be born again?"

00:02:51.640 --> 00:02:54.160
And He said it so clearly ! It's so clear.

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:58.040
Those who don't want to see can remain blind,

00:02:58.520 --> 00:03:01.120
but he said it very very clearly;

00:03:01.320 --> 00:03:05.120
that "No, that is,

00:03:05.160 --> 00:03:09.400
whatever is born of the flesh is the flesh,

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:16.120
but whatever is born of the Spirit is the Spirit."

00:03:17.880 --> 00:03:21.120
I mean nothing could be more clear than that,

00:03:21.160 --> 00:03:27.120
that it has to be born 'of the Spirit'.

00:03:27.520 --> 00:03:30.280
Of course, human beings have a special capacity

00:03:30.560 --> 00:03:32.760
to twist everything around.

00:03:32.880 --> 00:03:35.120
For them Spirit could be a book,

00:03:35.280 --> 00:03:39.280
could be some words, could be an organisation, a church,

00:03:39.400 --> 00:03:42.880
or some sort of a thing like that which they have made.

00:03:43.120 --> 00:03:46.520
But whatever is man-made

00:03:46.680 --> 00:03:49.120
is not the Spirit;

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:51.120
this is the clear

00:03:51.440 --> 00:03:55.480
statement of Christ, which people wanted to avoid and start

00:03:55.640 --> 00:04:00.320
their own organisations, their own ideas

00:04:00.920 --> 00:04:07.240
and created a very mythical thing in His name.

00:04:07.520 --> 00:04:12.120
And now the time has come for it to be blasted.

00:04:13.240 --> 00:04:17.560
It has been going on and on now for thousands of years,

00:04:17.920 --> 00:04:20.400
captured so many innocent people,

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:23.280
and people are into it.

00:04:24.440 --> 00:04:27.520
But when you are resurrected,

00:04:27.920 --> 00:04:31.240
when you become realised souls,

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:34.520
one has to understand that

00:04:34.680 --> 00:04:39.400
now your movement is

00:04:39.760 --> 00:04:41.960
inward,

00:04:42.280 --> 00:04:45.760
you are moving towards your roots and not outside.

00:04:45.920 --> 00:04:52.720
So whatever was the endeavour

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:56.120
before realisation

00:04:56.360 --> 00:05:00.640
has to be changed; the direction has to be changed.

00:05:00.840 --> 00:05:05.120
And that point mostly we miss.

00:05:06.760 --> 00:05:12.680
This is the thing today I am trying to explain to you:

00:05:12.960 --> 00:05:18.480
that so far to a human mind

00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:22.640
entertainment was important; entertaining

00:05:22.760 --> 00:05:26.360
to the mind, not to the Spirit.

00:05:26.760 --> 00:05:29.120
Entertainment to the Spirit

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:32.920
is absolutely opposite

00:05:33.120 --> 00:05:37.240
to the entertainment to the mind.

00:05:38.200 --> 00:05:43.040
Like somebody the other day telephoned to me and said

00:05:43.120 --> 00:05:49.120
that, "Mother, there is no excitement in Sahaja Yoga."

00:05:55.160 --> 00:05:59.800
See, excitement is too much.

00:06:00.120 --> 00:06:04.200
We are going against that.

00:06:04.760 --> 00:06:07.120
We are going towards peace,

00:06:07.120 --> 00:06:10.120
not towards excitement and this kind of electric shocks

00:06:10.200 --> 00:06:12.640
that we require every time.

00:06:12.840 --> 00:06:15.640
See a drunkard

00:06:15.800 --> 00:06:19.240
is alright in the morning but evening-time he goes off,

00:06:19.360 --> 00:06:21.800
he needs a shock,

00:06:22.040 --> 00:06:24.880
some sort of an injection into his body.

00:06:25.080 --> 00:06:30.520
'All' human enterprises have been like that, they are

00:06:30.680 --> 00:06:33.240
to excite your body.

00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:37.600
Because if it is the dead you are dealing with,

00:06:37.760 --> 00:06:42.120
then you have to excite it. But something that is living,

00:06:42.120 --> 00:06:47.720
that is eternal, you have to enjoy it and not excite it.

00:06:47.840 --> 00:06:52.120
So the direction has to be

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:59.880
juxtaposition, and that is where many Sahaja yogis fail to understand.

00:07:01.800 --> 00:07:05.280
"How do we do it ?" is the point.

00:07:05.920 --> 00:07:11.200
"How do we make our attention move inward

00:07:11.440 --> 00:07:14.640
instead of going outward."

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:17.640
If you start

00:07:18.400 --> 00:07:23.680
from the time you are born again, it is much easier,

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:29.680
because it is a new venture into you go in, that is the peace.

00:07:29.920 --> 00:07:34.120
Peace of your Spirit, the joy of your Spirit,

00:07:35.120 --> 00:07:39.200
which is permanent, you don't need any excitement from it, it is permanent,

00:07:39.320 --> 00:07:42.360
it is eternal.

00:07:44.680 --> 00:07:48.120
So the first thing that comes to our mind is,

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:51.120
that whatever we do

00:07:51.920 --> 00:07:58.120
before realisation we have not to do.

00:07:58.680 --> 00:08:01.200
The first and foremost thing is

00:08:01.320 --> 00:08:04.920
realisation comes to you effortlessly.

00:08:05.400 --> 00:08:08.520
So the effort which is built into your body

00:08:08.640 --> 00:08:11.000
all the time, the energy of effort,

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:12.840
"I must do this, I must do that,

00:08:12.960 --> 00:08:14.920
I have to do this, I have to do that," -

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:18.960
that creates tension - that I have told you already.

00:08:19.200 --> 00:08:24.200
So what do we do?

00:08:24.440 --> 00:08:28.440
We do not try

00:08:30.280 --> 00:08:35.520
to compete with others,

00:08:35.800 --> 00:08:39.640
we do not try

00:08:40.160 --> 00:08:49.840
to fix certain timing, dates, watches.

00:08:50.120 --> 00:08:55.120
We do not also put our attention

00:08:55.560 --> 00:08:59.000
into any endeavour

00:08:59.120 --> 00:09:03.000
which puts us into effort.

00:09:03.120 --> 00:09:08.120
But we relax that attitude of effort.

00:09:08.160 --> 00:09:10.160
It's called in Sanskrit

00:09:10.280 --> 00:09:12.120
as 'Prayatna Shaithilya'.

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:16.280
For a western mind it is very difficult to grasp the subject;

00:09:17.000 --> 00:09:19.680
so try to understand.

00:09:20.280 --> 00:09:22.680
That doesn't mean lethargy,

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:25.120
doesn't mean lethargy.

00:09:25.280 --> 00:09:29.880
So you should never confuse with the dead,

00:09:31.400 --> 00:09:33.400
the energy of the living.

00:09:33.520 --> 00:09:39.760
Now we are trying to transform our energies

00:09:40.280 --> 00:09:43.120
towards the energy of the Spirit.

00:09:44.120 --> 00:09:49.080
So you have to allow the Spirit to take over.

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:53.120
Your effort of your mind

00:09:53.120 --> 00:09:55.120
should be reduced

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:59.560
and the energy of the Spirit should work through you.

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:03.120
Now how do you do it?

00:10:06.760 --> 00:10:11.400
First is detachment.

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:15.360
Detachment.

00:10:15.840 --> 00:10:21.840
Detachment starts with the thought; let us see the thought.

00:10:22.320 --> 00:10:26.480
It is called as 'Vichara Shaithilya', relaxation of the thought.

00:10:26.760 --> 00:10:30.120
Now a thought is coming into your mind;

00:10:30.680 --> 00:10:33.120
some thought : "Today is Mother's puja let's go.

00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:35.280
We have to hurry up, you see. We must get this.

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:36.880
You didn't get the flowers,

00:10:36.920 --> 00:10:39.440
now you go to the 3rd world and get the flowers.

00:10:39.600 --> 00:10:42.440
You must get this and you must get that".

00:10:42.640 --> 00:10:48.320
Second is: "No, detach yourself.

00:10:51.800 --> 00:10:53.360
Witness.

00:10:55.120 --> 00:10:58.120
Leave it to the Spirit;

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:01.680
watch, you will get it."

00:11:01.840 --> 00:11:04.800
Many of you have noticed this.

00:11:05.120 --> 00:11:07.720
But still this mind which is quite silly

00:11:07.840 --> 00:11:12.120
tries to impress upon you that

00:11:12.160 --> 00:11:15.240
you have to use the old

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:19.200
junky instrument of this mind.

00:11:20.040 --> 00:11:22.280
And it asserts, that "Better use."

00:11:22.400 --> 00:11:25.200
And when you start using that,

00:11:25.360 --> 00:11:28.920
ego comes in, you get attached to it,

00:11:30.640 --> 00:11:33.120
and what you lose

00:11:33.120 --> 00:11:38.280
is your progress - and thus the joy is minimised.

00:11:38.400 --> 00:11:42.120
"How do you detach yourself ?"

00:11:42.560 --> 00:11:46.120
For a person who is absolutely detached, it's very difficult

00:11:46.120 --> 00:11:50.120
to explain "how to detach", isn't it?

00:11:51.080 --> 00:11:52.240
I'll try!

00:11:52.360 --> 00:11:57.280
Now. I cannot get attached, that the problem is.

00:12:01.520 --> 00:12:04.080
And I find it difficult to explain

00:12:04.120 --> 00:12:06.720
to you in words, which are human words,

00:12:06.840 --> 00:12:10.120
but still, I'll try to say now.

00:12:13.920 --> 00:12:17.920
Say, I tried something as human beings do, in the beginning,

00:12:18.040 --> 00:12:22.120
just to see how it works out - because I had to experiment.

00:12:22.280 --> 00:12:24.760
For example, when I had to,

00:12:24.880 --> 00:12:28.680
say, attend any puja or anything,

00:12:28.800 --> 00:12:34.320
I used to ask them, 'what is the auspicious time ?'

00:12:36.200 --> 00:12:39.840
So they would tell me, this is the auspicious time,

00:12:39.960 --> 00:12:41.720
then another would telephone to say

00:12:41.840 --> 00:12:43.400
"this is the auspicious time".

00:12:43.600 --> 00:12:46.080
So I said, how can there be two auspicious times? You see.

00:12:46.120 --> 00:12:47.920
It's a big problem with human beings.

00:12:48.040 --> 00:12:52.240
So they said - there are 5 Panchangas in India;

00:12:52.360 --> 00:12:57.120
means 5 books to consult the auspicious time.

00:12:57.280 --> 00:13:01.120
That's what human beings have done. I said, "Then why consult?

00:13:01.120 --> 00:13:05.400
It's better not to have 5 auspicious times, isn't it?"

00:13:05.520 --> 00:13:07.520
Then the auspicious time

00:13:07.640 --> 00:13:12.680
has to be beyond time.

00:13:13.560 --> 00:13:17.160
But it is bound in the time the way

00:13:17.400 --> 00:13:19.240
human beings have made it,

00:13:19.360 --> 00:13:23.720
so it is bound in the time. Like in India, it is so much, so much, so much,

00:13:23.840 --> 00:13:26.600
but now, here it is different.

00:13:26.760 --> 00:13:29.000
Then you calculate, - you have a watch.

00:13:29.120 --> 00:13:31.160
You see, to overcome all these hurdles

00:13:31.240 --> 00:13:34.200
human beings also make certain devices.

00:13:34.320 --> 00:13:38.640
So you consult. Now what is the auspicious time here?

00:13:38.920 --> 00:13:45.000
Leave at that time. Then it's a big headache.

00:13:45.120 --> 00:13:48.880
Because there are 5 books to be consulted,

00:13:49.000 --> 00:13:53.040
watch could be wrong, this could be wrong, that could be so.

00:13:53.120 --> 00:13:56.000
But if you are the Spirit,

00:13:56.120 --> 00:14:01.080
then the Spirit works out auspiciousness.

00:14:01.120 --> 00:14:04.360
It's the Spirit that works out auspiciousness.

00:14:04.560 --> 00:14:09.120
And imagine when you think like that, how much tension goes out.

00:14:09.440 --> 00:14:12.200
First of all you have to be a slave of your watch;

00:14:12.360 --> 00:14:15.000
another, you have to be a slave of the books;

00:14:15.120 --> 00:14:19.280
then you have to be a slave of the market,

00:14:20.280 --> 00:14:24.920
of the room, of the place which you have to hire.

00:14:26.080 --> 00:14:28.560
But supposing if you allow

00:14:28.760 --> 00:14:31.360
the Spirit to work it out,

00:14:32.080 --> 00:14:36.960
then 'everything' will work out. And you will reach at this point when

00:14:37.080 --> 00:14:39.640
it is the most auspicious.

00:14:40.040 --> 00:14:42.320
So how do you accept it ? -

00:14:42.560 --> 00:14:45.800
Just by accepting.

00:14:47.120 --> 00:14:50.120
So just now, if you give up

00:14:50.200 --> 00:14:54.120
your 'satta', your own domain;

00:14:54.280 --> 00:14:57.960
you get into the domain of your Spirit.

00:14:59.120 --> 00:15:02.120
You give up 'your' domain,

00:15:02.440 --> 00:15:04.920
that is, your ego's domain,

00:15:05.040 --> 00:15:06.800
or may be your super-ego's domain,

00:15:06.920 --> 00:15:10.040
you give up that and try

00:15:10.120 --> 00:15:14.120
to see things how it works out.

00:15:14.280 --> 00:15:17.560
Now, what is the testing point of it?

00:15:17.880 --> 00:15:23.320
How do you test it ? It works out -

00:15:24.120 --> 00:15:30.120
that's the point of testing it. It works out.

00:15:30.400 --> 00:15:36.120
Allow it to work out. Don't put your attention.

00:15:36.280 --> 00:15:40.200
Attention has the second part of is the tension.

00:15:40.360 --> 00:15:44.040
And don't try to say, "Why not today,

00:15:44.120 --> 00:15:45.880
it should have happened today,

00:15:46.040 --> 00:15:48.120
we expected it to happen;

00:15:48.120 --> 00:15:50.560
why not at 'this' moment ?" -

00:15:50.680 --> 00:15:53.440
That's your ego.

00:15:53.600 --> 00:15:57.760
"Thy will be done".

00:15:59.120 --> 00:16:02.200
So the thought

00:16:02.640 --> 00:16:05.960
that starts moving

00:16:06.080 --> 00:16:10.200
in our mind all the time, which creates tensions

00:16:10.440 --> 00:16:13.480
is not the thought of the Spirit.

00:16:13.840 --> 00:16:17.640
So, what you should say, "Not this thought.

00:16:17.840 --> 00:16:22.400
Not this thought. /?/.

00:16:22.600 --> 00:16:26.800
Not this thought, not this thought, not this thought", -

00:16:27.440 --> 00:16:30.680
and see how you relax - Now you are relaxing. -

00:16:31.040 --> 00:16:34.000
'Not this thought, not this thought, ...

00:16:34.120 --> 00:16:38.920
Just go on refusing accepting any thought.

00:16:39.120 --> 00:16:41.160
So you go into Nirvichara.

00:16:41.320 --> 00:16:45.960
In that state you feel the Spirit.

00:16:46.680 --> 00:16:49.240
Christ has done the greatest work

00:16:49.400 --> 00:16:52.920
on this, I should say, but we do not understand because

00:16:53.040 --> 00:16:58.240
His life was like a micro thing you see, in 3 years...

00:16:58.440 --> 00:17:03.120
So we have to open it out a little bit and see what He did.

00:17:03.360 --> 00:17:07.840
He has given us the greatest weapon of "forgiveness".

00:17:08.800 --> 00:17:14.120
When you forgive a person, what do you do?

00:17:15.040 --> 00:17:17.880
You accept the situation, to begin with.

00:17:18.000 --> 00:17:21.840
And secondly you forgive

00:17:23.400 --> 00:17:27.320
what you think has been done wrong to you.

00:17:27.680 --> 00:17:33.320
But because nothing can be done wrong to your Spirit,

00:17:33.560 --> 00:17:37.120
you just forgive, because you are the Spirit.

00:17:38.840 --> 00:17:41.120
And when you forgive,

00:17:41.120 --> 00:17:45.480
you have found that your tension goes away.

00:17:45.920 --> 00:17:50.120
So even to your thoughts if you say, "Alright. Forgive this thought,

00:17:50.120 --> 00:17:51.560
forgive this thought," -

00:17:51.680 --> 00:17:55.360
because thought is also not to be punished.

00:17:55.880 --> 00:17:58.200
Forgive this thought, forgive this thought,

00:17:58.320 --> 00:18:00.280
forgive everything.

00:18:00.400 --> 00:18:03.840
Not forget, - forgive;

00:18:05.080 --> 00:18:08.480
because then you will even forget that you are the Spirit!

00:18:11.920 --> 00:18:13.920
But forgive

00:18:14.120 --> 00:18:16.080
"all the thoughts that are coming to me,"

00:18:16.120 --> 00:18:19.080
just go on saying. This is a mantra.

00:18:19.120 --> 00:18:23.160
What is a mantra? - Is that power

00:18:23.280 --> 00:18:28.520
of the word, that expresses Spirit.

00:18:30.160 --> 00:18:34.080
So this is a very important thing Christ has given us:

00:18:34.120 --> 00:18:36.120
the weapon of forgiveness.

00:18:36.280 --> 00:18:38.600
Everybody has that weapon,

00:18:38.880 --> 00:18:41.120
everyone can use that weapon.

00:18:41.120 --> 00:18:44.600
You don't have to put in any effort for it.

00:18:44.720 --> 00:18:47.120
You don't have to pay for it,

00:18:47.160 --> 00:18:50.320
it is just that you have to say "I forgive."

00:18:50.680 --> 00:18:53.960
You'll be amazed your nerves will soothe down,

00:18:54.080 --> 00:18:57.080
this tension,

00:18:57.120 --> 00:19:03.280
this pressure of these modern things

00:19:03.400 --> 00:19:08.520
will be reduced if you go on saying "I forgive", "I forgive them".

00:19:08.640 --> 00:19:12.520
For example, you go and see,

00:19:12.800 --> 00:19:13.920
a some sort of a...

00:19:14.040 --> 00:19:17.200
I mean if you happen suddenly to see something very filthy,

00:19:17.320 --> 00:19:20.880
according to the Spirit

00:19:21.120 --> 00:19:23.120
may be it is very exciting

00:19:23.120 --> 00:19:27.520
according to normal human beings, but we are abnormal people

00:19:27.840 --> 00:19:31.360
and for us if we find it rather ugly

00:19:31.560 --> 00:19:34.800
then - the best thing is to get over is "I forgive,

00:19:34.920 --> 00:19:38.000
because they are ignorant, they are blind,

00:19:38.120 --> 00:19:40.440
they are not yet there where I am.

00:19:40.560 --> 00:19:45.040
I am the one who is at the source of enjoyment,

00:19:45.120 --> 00:19:48.000
at the source of peace and while these are not.

00:19:48.160 --> 00:19:51.160
So I forgive."

00:19:53.440 --> 00:19:58.640
And you'll be amazed that this forgiveness that Christ gives you,

00:19:59.360 --> 00:20:07.080
works out Vichara Shaithilya, is the relaxation of the thought.

00:20:09.960 --> 00:20:17.040
Now this opposite movement that you have to move, first of all

00:20:17.120 --> 00:20:23.120
should start at this point, today, from forgiving others.

00:20:25.120 --> 00:20:28.160
Now what happens when you forgive someone?

00:20:28.280 --> 00:20:30.920
That means you do not react.

00:20:31.040 --> 00:20:38.360
The power to react to somebody's injuries, insults

00:20:38.640 --> 00:20:42.400
is finished. And when that power is finished,

00:20:42.520 --> 00:20:45.440
you become a powerful person;

00:20:45.680 --> 00:20:49.120
because nobody can now

00:20:52.000 --> 00:20:57.760
overpower you; because nobody can kill you, nobody can hurt you,

00:20:58.080 --> 00:21:00.840
nobody can do anything to you.

00:21:01.880 --> 00:21:04.720
But it is not, again I'll say, shamelessness.

00:21:04.840 --> 00:21:09.120
You see people can think that it is shamelessness.

00:21:10.800 --> 00:21:15.760
So if somebody says to you something harsh

00:21:16.880 --> 00:21:22.160
and something that is wrong, you do not accept it.

00:21:22.560 --> 00:21:25.640
But supposing I shout at someone, the bhoots run away.

00:21:25.760 --> 00:21:29.440
You have seen that many a times, I have to shout at people,

00:21:29.560 --> 00:21:31.480
so bhoots run away because they react,

00:21:31.600 --> 00:21:37.400
and they just run away, but the Spirit shines through.

00:21:38.760 --> 00:21:42.720
So in Sahaja Yoga one has to understand that

00:21:42.840 --> 00:21:46.360
it is just this central path,

00:21:46.600 --> 00:21:49.480
is just the balancing thing which is important

00:21:49.600 --> 00:21:52.960
it's not an extreme of anything.

00:21:53.200 --> 00:21:57.120
Like when we go to say that you must forgive everyone -

00:21:57.400 --> 00:22:00.640
is not going to that extreme

00:22:00.760 --> 00:22:02.920
where you have done some wrong,

00:22:03.040 --> 00:22:05.920
and somebody says to you, you don't take that part of it;

00:22:06.040 --> 00:22:07.760
it doesn't mean that.

00:22:08.000 --> 00:22:13.120
Again discretion is the engine of your movement.

00:22:13.320 --> 00:22:18.000
So you have to see that, "if they have said it,

00:22:18.840 --> 00:22:24.680
something like that, is it, have I gone against the Spirit?"

00:22:25.000 --> 00:22:26.920
Otherwise, if I say to you something,

00:22:27.040 --> 00:22:29.920
you will say, "Alright, forgive Mother." -

00:22:30.120 --> 00:22:35.000
You see the point ! "Forgive Her for saying so". No.

00:22:36.880 --> 00:22:41.120
You cannot say that to me.

00:22:42.120 --> 00:22:48.600
So then, that is the point you start thinking,

00:22:50.000 --> 00:22:52.800
"Why Mother said so? What have I done?"

00:22:52.920 --> 00:22:55.640
Now think on those lines; so you start moving again.

00:22:55.920 --> 00:22:58.480
It's a very

00:22:59.600 --> 00:23:02.120
thin road on which you have to walk.

00:23:02.800 --> 00:23:08.240
One side is the huge big Gibraltar,

00:23:08.360 --> 00:23:11.000
rock of Gibraltar of your ego,

00:23:11.120 --> 00:23:14.080
and another side is the super-ego.

00:23:14.160 --> 00:23:19.280
In between is the small discretion path going,

00:23:19.520 --> 00:23:22.680
on which you have to see both the sides.

00:23:23.280 --> 00:23:26.920
Whether you are hitting yourself

00:23:27.120 --> 00:23:30.080
with the rock of Gibraltar, or you are falling into the

00:23:30.120 --> 00:23:33.200
valley of super-ego,

00:23:33.320 --> 00:23:37.760
you should see that you are using your discretion.

00:23:37.880 --> 00:23:41.800
So, the another thing one has to remember

00:23:41.960 --> 00:23:46.320
is that whatever you were doing before realization, is to go to extremes.

00:23:46.400 --> 00:23:51.680
For example now, you start some sort of a movement.

00:23:51.920 --> 00:23:54.680
Say, you say we'll have classical things.

00:23:54.800 --> 00:23:59.160
Alright. Then you go so classical that it becomes mechanical.

00:23:59.720 --> 00:24:02.120
Now you say, "Give up; we'll start anticulture".

00:24:02.160 --> 00:24:05.600
So you'll go to the other side that you become primitive.

00:24:05.760 --> 00:24:07.880
Till you have reached the end of it

00:24:08.000 --> 00:24:11.120
and learnt a lesson of your life, you do not return.

00:24:11.400 --> 00:24:14.680
But in Sahaja Yoga, it's a very slippery road

00:24:14.800 --> 00:24:16.760
on which we are walking.

00:24:18.320 --> 00:24:19.800
And there you have to see

00:24:19.920 --> 00:24:23.320
that it is not your ego and it is not your super-ego.

00:24:23.520 --> 00:24:26.280
So discretion has to be used

00:24:26.360 --> 00:24:29.760
very much, and the balance, in this movement

00:24:29.880 --> 00:24:35.120
which we need not use otherwise,

00:24:35.120 --> 00:24:37.640
till we are absolutely destroyed

00:24:37.760 --> 00:24:41.200
we can go ahead with it, before realization.

00:24:41.320 --> 00:24:45.960
But in Sahaja Yoga as soon as you leave your discretion

00:24:46.080 --> 00:24:48.640
you fall this side or that side.

00:24:49.160 --> 00:24:54.120
Now those people who are of high quality

00:24:54.120 --> 00:24:57.440
Sahaja yogis take to discretion first:

00:24:57.600 --> 00:24:59.280
"How far to go?"

00:24:59.440 --> 00:25:04.120
Now for that Mother doesn't have to say because you are the Spirit.

00:25:04.400 --> 00:25:06.440
You yourself, you are the Spirit.

00:25:06.560 --> 00:25:09.280
First of all assume your position as the Spirit,

00:25:09.400 --> 00:25:11.520
and then you move with it,

00:25:11.640 --> 00:25:16.000
that you say discretely "how far to go,

00:25:16.120 --> 00:25:18.280
how far not to go."

00:25:20.280 --> 00:25:25.120
Now that is one of the things, that you have to become thoughtless,

00:25:25.200 --> 00:25:28.080
by becoming

00:25:28.520 --> 00:25:31.080
a forgiving person.

00:25:31.440 --> 00:25:35.120
Most of the thoughts will drop out once you become forgiving.

00:25:35.120 --> 00:25:37.560
But you cannot forgive some people, like you

00:25:37.680 --> 00:25:40.640
cannot forgive God, you cannot forgive Mother.

00:25:40.760 --> 00:25:43.120
Certain things you cannot do,

00:25:43.120 --> 00:25:46.120
so the Maryadas must be seen.

00:25:47.520 --> 00:25:54.320
Now, in these boundaries if you walk properly, you can go ahead.

00:25:55.480 --> 00:26:00.120
This is the thing which brings you 'Vichara Shaithilya' or you can call

00:26:00.160 --> 00:26:04.840
the mind becomes relaxed.

00:26:05.680 --> 00:26:08.480
Then you have to have "Vishaya Shaithilya"

00:26:08.600 --> 00:26:11.120
means, your organs, sense organs

00:26:11.120 --> 00:26:13.200
always react to things,

00:26:13.320 --> 00:26:17.120
because you are human beings, you see, you are born like that.

00:26:17.120 --> 00:26:20.440
So whatever happens,

00:26:21.560 --> 00:26:23.240
you react.

00:26:23.400 --> 00:26:29.440
For example, you see a beautiful flower, you react.

00:26:29.680 --> 00:26:33.720
Some sort of a thought rises with it.

00:26:35.320 --> 00:26:38.240
Now you must practice

00:26:38.400 --> 00:26:43.320
to see something without allowing any thought to rise.

00:26:43.800 --> 00:26:46.800
Then you start sucking

00:26:46.920 --> 00:26:50.040
through your Spirit the beauty,

00:26:50.120 --> 00:26:51.920
the glory,

00:26:52.040 --> 00:26:56.120
the fragrance of a flower:

00:26:56.680 --> 00:27:00.600
Every flower is a poetry,

00:27:01.120 --> 00:27:05.120
but when you start thinking about it

00:27:06.040 --> 00:27:09.320
then it becomes a dead thing.

00:27:09.440 --> 00:27:11.960
But you just try to enjoy.

00:27:12.080 --> 00:27:15.040
Now you are the people who are

00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:19.200
on this earth to enjoy yourself,

00:27:19.560 --> 00:27:24.040
not to worry about anything, just enjoy.

00:27:30.800 --> 00:27:34.840
But if you are still used to,

00:27:36.400 --> 00:27:38.280
"I must do this thing special,

00:27:38.400 --> 00:27:40.800
I am something special Sahaja yogi,

00:27:40.960 --> 00:27:46.560
I am a very highly evolved Sahaja yogi", then you are finished.

00:27:47.960 --> 00:27:52.480
Say, we are all going in a boat; enjoy the boat!

00:27:52.560 --> 00:27:56.280
And also the waves. But somebody says. "I am a very special one,

00:27:56.400 --> 00:27:58.800
I'll try to jump down,"

00:28:01.200 --> 00:28:03.720
then you are back again

00:28:03.960 --> 00:28:06.120
into the same position.

00:28:06.320 --> 00:28:11.040
So one has to have an attitude of looking at things

00:28:11.120 --> 00:28:13.120
try to develop this habit

00:28:13.200 --> 00:28:17.960
of looking at things without thinking about it.

00:28:18.120 --> 00:28:23.720
Try to develop your mind on those lines; that you do not react.

00:28:23.880 --> 00:28:27.280
Now the excitement business,

00:28:27.400 --> 00:28:32.400
or all this sensationalisation that is today's craze,

00:28:32.480 --> 00:28:36.560
comes from the same - that your sense organs

00:28:36.640 --> 00:28:41.200
require a kind of sensation because they react.

00:28:41.320 --> 00:28:44.480
While we must have our sense organs which do not react;

00:28:45.120 --> 00:28:49.880
because they must only react to the Spirit.

00:28:50.040 --> 00:28:53.960
So we have to develop a new type of sense organs

00:28:54.120 --> 00:28:58.320
or a new quality of sense organs

00:28:58.560 --> 00:29:04.120
who do not react to outside excitement.

00:29:04.880 --> 00:29:08.880
Now if you want Sahaja Yoga to be excitement, how can it be?

00:29:08.960 --> 00:29:12.560
I mean, just, it is just the opposite.

00:29:15.400 --> 00:29:18.880
So what you have to do is to

00:29:19.400 --> 00:29:23.800
see that your sense organs - say for example your eyes,

00:29:24.480 --> 00:29:29.120
they see something - then they react;

00:29:29.400 --> 00:29:34.720
your ears, they hear something - they react;

00:29:35.640 --> 00:29:42.400
somebody wants to talk and see the reaction.

00:29:43.200 --> 00:29:47.400
There are expectations.

00:29:48.480 --> 00:29:54.560
But because Spirit is active

00:29:54.960 --> 00:30:01.720
itself it acts itself, you have seen vibrations don't speak, they act.

00:30:02.120 --> 00:30:05.200
It has the power to act,

00:30:05.400 --> 00:30:08.560
you need not react.

00:30:10.400 --> 00:30:16.640
If you can reduce the power of reaction,

00:30:16.960 --> 00:30:20.320
you rise much higher.

00:30:20.400 --> 00:30:24.600
This is a thing which one has to know,

00:30:24.720 --> 00:30:29.800
when now we are celebrating His resurrection

00:30:29.960 --> 00:30:32.480
because it is Tapa,

00:30:32.640 --> 00:30:35.280
it is the penance of Christ.

00:30:35.400 --> 00:30:38.320
Christ came on this earth for penance.

00:30:38.440 --> 00:30:41.800
You know in the Gayatri mantra,

00:30:41.960 --> 00:30:44.400
there are 7 things they have said it,

00:30:44.400 --> 00:30:46.400
and at the point of Christ

00:30:46.400 --> 00:30:49.960
it is Tapa, is the penance.

00:30:50.200 --> 00:30:55.880
So you have to have the so-called penance to achieve the joy.

00:30:56.120 --> 00:31:00.800
The penance is to pull back

00:31:00.960 --> 00:31:04.280
your sense organs inside yourself. As Krishna has said

00:31:04.400 --> 00:31:06.640
that you have to pull back

00:31:06.800 --> 00:31:15.560
all your limbs of sense organs like a tortoise does.

00:31:17.040 --> 00:31:23.480
So the excitement that you require

00:31:24.200 --> 00:31:30.400
for your sense organs is no more needed,

00:31:30.640 --> 00:31:40.200
because your sense organs now, are themselves the source of excitement.

00:31:42.320 --> 00:31:48.280
In the sense that they neutralize all the excitements.

00:31:51.040 --> 00:31:55.560
You go to that point from where it starts.

00:31:57.280 --> 00:32:00.640
A river starts with a very small, little drop,

00:32:00.800 --> 00:32:04.400
and then it expands, expands, expands, expands.

00:32:04.400 --> 00:32:09.880
You go to the source. Absolutely to the central point.

00:32:10.480 --> 00:32:15.480
There you'll find hardly even a drop falling out.

00:32:16.400 --> 00:32:21.960
Another good example would be a wheel,

00:32:22.200 --> 00:32:24.200
it has the central point.

00:32:24.320 --> 00:32:28.400
And the wheel moves all the time but the central point has to be fixed,

00:32:28.400 --> 00:32:34.400
otherwise with the wheel that central point also moves,

00:32:34.480 --> 00:32:37.280
then the cart cannot move,

00:32:37.400 --> 00:32:39.720
the cart will also start rolling down.

00:32:39.880 --> 00:32:43.640
So the central point has to be fixed,

00:32:43.720 --> 00:32:46.200
otherwise the wheel cannot move.

00:32:46.320 --> 00:32:51.960
So you go to that central point, and the movement is on the central point,

00:32:52.120 --> 00:32:58.400
where there is no movement,

00:32:58.400 --> 00:33:05.040
in a way, because there is only ascent, there's no revolution,

00:33:05.280 --> 00:33:11.120
it doesn't revolve any more, there's just ascent on the central point.

00:33:12.400 --> 00:33:14.480
I hope you try to understand,

00:33:14.640 --> 00:33:18.400
that all the movements come out of ignorance.

00:33:18.640 --> 00:33:20.720
All the outer movements come

00:33:20.800 --> 00:33:25.400
because we are not yet on the central point.

00:33:25.400 --> 00:33:29.800
But that

00:33:29.960 --> 00:33:33.400
achievement is not difficult because you have jumped onto it -

00:33:33.400 --> 00:33:37.200
but you again come out onto the periphery,

00:33:37.400 --> 00:33:39.800
onto the wheel.

00:33:39.960 --> 00:33:42.720
So how to keep there,

00:33:42.880 --> 00:33:44.720
and to ascend in that, line.

00:33:44.880 --> 00:33:48.320
Say, for example, there are wheels - like this wheels after - wheels;

00:33:48.400 --> 00:33:54.720
but the central point is fixed. Now every time you jump out,

00:33:55.040 --> 00:33:58.280
now how do you go back to the central point? -

00:33:58.400 --> 00:34:07.200
is by detachment, by Tapa, by penance.

00:34:07.960 --> 00:34:12.400
Penance is "to deny."

00:34:13.880 --> 00:34:17.240
It doesn't mean asceticism of outside

00:34:17.320 --> 00:34:21.240
but asceticism of within.

00:34:23.480 --> 00:34:27.720
First of all we must learn to give.

00:34:31.200 --> 00:34:34.400
Give to others.

00:34:36.400 --> 00:34:39.320
That also sometimes people find it difficult, I have seen.

00:34:39.400 --> 00:34:41.640
Even to give one pound - they say -

00:34:41.720 --> 00:34:46.560
for Sahaja Yoga people find it difficult, I was amazed!

00:34:48.720 --> 00:34:55.200
So to give to others is going to be even worse.

00:34:55.400 --> 00:35:00.640
Try to give to others. Detachment.

00:35:01.400 --> 00:35:09.880
So one way is to have forgiveness,

00:35:10.800 --> 00:35:16.960
then second is generosity.

00:35:20.400 --> 00:35:26.120
If you work for Sahaja Yoga : "I haven't done anything so far".

00:35:26.280 --> 00:35:29.320
Not to react to it what work you have done.

00:35:29.400 --> 00:35:32.400
"Oh, it's a pleasure, I did it. It's my pleasure, I did it.

00:35:32.720 --> 00:35:34.400
Just out of pleasure".

00:35:34.960 --> 00:35:41.640
Don't count it; "I brought four flowers, she brought two flowers.

00:35:42.280 --> 00:35:46.400
I must be paid for one and a half flower."

00:35:46.560 --> 00:35:50.320
All these calculations are

00:35:50.560 --> 00:35:52.560
on the periphery, outside,

00:35:52.680 --> 00:35:53.960
when you were not realized souls.

00:35:54.040 --> 00:35:59.960
Now you just don't count anything else, but your blessings.

00:36:00.400 --> 00:36:03.400
So you be generous.

00:36:03.960 --> 00:36:10.400
I have seen now people have different attachments, subtler ones.

00:36:10.400 --> 00:36:15.200
Like attached to their own children I've seen people.

00:36:15.400 --> 00:36:17.640
Once their children are born to the Sahaja yogis

00:36:17.800 --> 00:36:21.560
then the whole world becomes their children:

00:36:22.200 --> 00:36:25.960
You spoil them, you spoil yourselves.

00:36:26.320 --> 00:36:32.800
You are just their trustees.

00:36:33.440 --> 00:36:36.360
But to you it becomes a very big

00:36:36.440 --> 00:36:38.280
thing that you have produced a child.

00:36:38.360 --> 00:36:39.800
Anybody can produce - even a dog

00:36:39.880 --> 00:36:41.720
produces a child, what is so great? -

00:36:41.960 --> 00:36:44.200
I mean, the bitch.

00:36:46.640 --> 00:36:50.400
That's a funny word to say!

00:36:52.280 --> 00:36:54.320
So, to create a child is not something great,

00:36:54.400 --> 00:36:59.400
but that you have a child in charge of you, which has to

00:37:01.960 --> 00:37:04.280
work for God.

00:37:04.400 --> 00:37:07.640
You are just in charge; but to identify that

00:37:07.880 --> 00:37:11.880
this child is great, it's a very big realized soul and

00:37:12.120 --> 00:37:15.280
all that, you see, will blast your head completely,

00:37:15.400 --> 00:37:20.480
because it's a subtler blasting. It's like hydrogen bomb.

00:37:20.560 --> 00:37:24.800
Ordinary bombs can destroy a part of it, but these subtler bombs

00:37:24.960 --> 00:37:26.280
are even worse.

00:37:26.400 --> 00:37:30.560
And this will spoil the child, that will spoil

00:37:30.880 --> 00:37:35.800
also you very much in your ascent.

00:37:36.120 --> 00:37:39.400
So what you have to do is to see that

00:37:39.480 --> 00:37:43.400
if you have a child, alright you are just in charge,

00:37:46.120 --> 00:37:50.040
as you are in charge of all, the children of Sahaja yogis

00:37:50.280 --> 00:37:53.480
not of your own. Be generous.

00:37:53.560 --> 00:37:56.560
/?/

00:37:56.640 --> 00:38:01.960
"The person who is a generous person. for him the whole world is his family."

00:38:02.280 --> 00:38:05.200
So expand yourself.

00:38:05.280 --> 00:38:07.880
This is my family, this is my wife,

00:38:07.960 --> 00:38:09.480
how can I live without my wife,

00:38:09.560 --> 00:38:13.040
or my husband my child; my -

00:38:13.200 --> 00:38:15.560
this will not help you.

00:38:15.640 --> 00:38:18.720
This will tie you down completely.

00:38:18.960 --> 00:38:25.200
This is a very subtler thing you start, because now you are receding back.

00:38:25.400 --> 00:38:26.960
First you gave up your family,

00:38:27.040 --> 00:38:29.200
gave up your children, gave up everything,

00:38:29.320 --> 00:38:31.200
came to this extreme; now you are going back.

00:38:31.320 --> 00:38:33.040
For Indians

00:38:33.120 --> 00:38:35.200
they understand that they are already too much in it,

00:38:35.280 --> 00:38:37.720
so they know that to detach yourself from your children is

00:38:37.880 --> 00:38:39.560
very important because they are already in it.

00:38:41.280 --> 00:38:43.800
They are too much attached to their children.

00:38:44.120 --> 00:38:46.480
In the beginning, they will always tell me, my child is like this,

00:38:46.640 --> 00:38:48.800
my mother is like this, my father is like this,

00:38:48.960 --> 00:38:52.400
my brother is like this, /?/ and they will be all bhoots,

00:38:52.400 --> 00:38:54.880
/?/ one better than the other.

00:38:55.640 --> 00:38:58.560
Without any discretion, bring all those relations on my head

00:38:58.720 --> 00:39:01.400
and I feel terrible about it.

00:39:01.480 --> 00:39:04.720
Even, a farfetched relation of a relation of a relation

00:39:04.880 --> 00:39:06.040
of a relation

00:39:06.200 --> 00:39:08.800
they will bring in along: "But you see she is my relation".

00:39:08.880 --> 00:39:12.040
So, in India it is very important that you are a relation

00:39:12.120 --> 00:39:13.720
of such and such person,

00:39:13.880 --> 00:39:16.280
and you may not have anything to do with that person.

00:39:16.400 --> 00:39:20.120
But he is a relation, so he is a relation.

00:39:21.960 --> 00:39:25.040
So, what we understand, is that

00:39:25.200 --> 00:39:30.800
our relationships and our identifications have to be dropped completely.

00:39:32.880 --> 00:39:36.960
We are universal beings now.

00:39:39.480 --> 00:39:41.480
So your child is a source of joy

00:39:41.560 --> 00:39:45.040
- every child should be the source of joy to you,

00:39:45.320 --> 00:39:47.120
every child should be.

00:39:47.200 --> 00:39:50.320
Bachelors that way are better or the ones who are not yet married,

00:39:50.400 --> 00:39:53.400
they can enjoy everybody's child nicely.

00:39:54.480 --> 00:39:57.720
But, when you are not a mother and a father,

00:39:57.880 --> 00:40:00.800
if you are enjoying, what is so creditable?

00:40:00.880 --> 00:40:05.400
When you become, the parents and then,

00:40:05.560 --> 00:40:07.480
you enjoy other children

00:40:07.560 --> 00:40:10.280
as much as you enjoy your child,

00:40:10.400 --> 00:40:12.880
then your generosity has started.

00:40:13.320 --> 00:40:17.640
So the generosity of loving others, the generosity

00:40:18.800 --> 00:40:20.720
through compassion.

00:40:20.880 --> 00:40:23.720
Compassion doesn't mean that you should pity someone but

00:40:23.880 --> 00:40:28.200
compassion means the sharing of

00:40:29.400 --> 00:40:33.560
personality, sharing of love personality.

00:40:33.720 --> 00:40:36.720
And that is where we miss the point,

00:40:36.880 --> 00:40:40.880
that compassion means that somebody has to be helped.

00:40:41.120 --> 00:40:43.400
Sahaja Yoga compassion is not that,

00:40:43.400 --> 00:40:47.280
Sahaja Yoga compassion is in sharing.

00:40:48.480 --> 00:40:51.960
Now the fourth thing you have to remember.

