01:01:13.880 --> 01:01:16.880
and he can correct everyone, and he can punish everyone

01:01:17.000 --> 01:01:20.800
and he can do as he likes, than he is not collective.

01:01:21.400 --> 01:01:23.640
But sometimes you have to also

01:01:23.800 --> 01:01:29.200
understand that even with bhootish people I have to stoop down to conquer them,

01:01:29.400 --> 01:01:31.400
to bring them round.

01:01:33.720 --> 01:01:38.320
Don't become like them; try to elevate them

01:01:38.400 --> 01:01:41.400
than to go down to their level.

01:01:42.480 --> 01:01:46.040
And if you can manage that, then you have achieved

01:01:46.120 --> 01:01:50.400
what you wanted to do through your collectivity.

01:01:50.640 --> 01:01:55.400
And a person has to be collective. If he is not collective

01:01:55.400 --> 01:02:01.400
then one must know that there is something definitely wrong with that person.

01:02:04.880 --> 01:02:11.120
Then, what you have to do after detachment from things -

01:02:11.400 --> 01:02:16.720
the penance part of it. For this we have to be

01:02:16.800 --> 01:02:20.960
doing some penance. For example, you are too much attached to any thing;

01:02:21.480 --> 01:02:25.120
say you are very fond of food. Many people are, I know that:

01:02:25.200 --> 01:02:27.200
the tongue is the worst of all.

01:02:27.640 --> 01:02:33.200
If you can control tongue then you have control over 50% of your sense organs.

01:02:33.480 --> 01:02:35.120
If you are attached to the tongue.

01:02:35.200 --> 01:02:37.960
These days I am going into a big penance, I am eating just

01:02:38.040 --> 01:02:41.880
boiled food without salt without any thing in it, just boiled food.

01:02:42.400 --> 01:02:48.320
Going into penance. I have to, for 9 months.

01:02:48.640 --> 01:02:49.720
For me it doesn't matter.

01:02:49.800 --> 01:02:53.800
It is no penance for me because I've no tongue at all.

01:02:53.960 --> 01:02:57.040
No taste buds. I can manage.

01:02:57.320 --> 01:02:59.200
So whatever you like too much,

01:02:59.320 --> 01:03:01.960
"Ahaa! I love to have something...," you see. Especially

01:03:02.080 --> 01:03:05.880
here I've seen if you see good food or anything - "Mmmm....."

01:03:09.480 --> 01:03:13.960
Now, it's as cold as ice, should I have it.

01:03:14.120 --> 01:03:16.080
I can, if you want

01:03:16.200 --> 01:03:20.160
but it's rather cool. Ithink you would to give me hot alright.

01:03:20.400 --> 01:03:22.400
I don't mind having it.

01:03:22.560 --> 01:03:28.200
Alright. So now what you have to do, is to have

01:03:28.400 --> 01:03:36.120
a kind of self-directed discipline.

01:03:36.200 --> 01:03:39.560
Self-directed, not on others.

01:03:40.480 --> 01:03:42.880
Self-directed.

01:03:44.320 --> 01:03:46.480
"Do I meditate in the morning?

01:03:46.640 --> 01:03:49.280
I don't. So what's wrong with me?

01:03:49.400 --> 01:03:52.120
I'm supposed to be a Sahaja yogi."

01:03:54.960 --> 01:04:00.640
Nobody has to tell you, you yourself should do this to yourself.

01:04:01.120 --> 01:04:04.400
You are fond of food, "Alright doesn't matter, I'll fast for two days".

01:04:04.480 --> 01:04:06.880
No fasting is allowed in Sahaja Yoga, alright;

01:04:07.120 --> 01:04:09.720
but fasting for detachment is alright.

01:04:09.880 --> 01:04:13.400
Not for God's Sake, but for your sake you do it.

01:04:14.280 --> 01:04:18.880
"I like a particular type of cake. Alright I'll not have it.

01:04:19.040 --> 01:04:20.480
I'll not have it for one year".

01:04:20.640 --> 01:04:24.720
But no, when people have to give up, they give up something like rhubarb!

01:04:34.040 --> 01:04:36.120
So one should not be cunning about it,

01:04:36.200 --> 01:04:38.560
you should not be cunning with yourself.

01:04:38.720 --> 01:04:43.640
So what you have to do is to see that where does this mind go?

01:04:43.960 --> 01:04:45.480
What is the attraction?

01:04:45.640 --> 01:04:49.400
I mean, even now I find some people are like Romeo and Juliets,

01:04:49.480 --> 01:04:53.560
you see, still living in that area of Romeo-Julietness. Get out of it!

01:04:54.200 --> 01:04:56.280
Nonsense.

01:05:00.400 --> 01:05:02.120
Get out of that kind of a thing.

01:05:02.280 --> 01:05:04.640
That doesn't mean you become a dry personality.

01:05:04.720 --> 01:05:06.800
Another extreme can be that

01:05:06.920 --> 01:05:09.480
you just become like sticks, that's not the point.

01:05:09.640 --> 01:05:15.320
But you should not indulge into these things.

01:05:15.960 --> 01:05:18.960
These are all artificial things.

01:05:19.400 --> 01:05:23.480
So a 'tapa' is to be established within yourself.

01:05:23.720 --> 01:05:27.400
Self-discipline. Now those who talk too much should stop talking.

01:05:27.480 --> 01:05:29.640
Absolutely mauna is the ilaj.

01:05:29.880 --> 01:05:34.400
Mauna is the treatment for such people! Just don't talk!

01:05:34.640 --> 01:05:37.800
Those who do not talk,

01:05:37.960 --> 01:05:41.120
most of the English men do not talk, women talk too much.

01:05:41.400 --> 01:05:43.280
It's a fact. I've seen -

01:05:43.400 --> 01:05:46.480
any interview you see, the women will talk first.

01:05:46.720 --> 01:05:49.040
This constable lady died; her mother was talking.

01:05:49.200 --> 01:05:51.960
In India the mother would not be in a position to talk, you know.

01:05:52.040 --> 01:05:53.880
The father was sitting quiet.

01:05:54.120 --> 01:05:58.120
You just can't imagine. In India supposing a child dies like that, you see,

01:05:58.200 --> 01:06:01.320
the mother would be absolutely sobbing, in a mess.

01:06:01.400 --> 01:06:04.400
She won't be talking. Here the woman was talking, we were most surprised!

01:06:04.640 --> 01:06:07.640
You see. The women talk too much

01:06:08.200 --> 01:06:11.480
the men just don't they are not supposed to talk I think,

01:06:12.400 --> 01:06:14.040
they just keep quiet.

01:06:14.200 --> 01:06:17.480
At the most they might be slapping. I don't know what they do.

01:06:20.400 --> 01:06:23.400
So what we have to do is to teach ourselves,

01:06:23.880 --> 01:06:28.400
that if our tongue talks too much then we'd better keep quiet.

01:06:28.880 --> 01:06:32.400
If we do not talk, we better talk.

01:06:32.480 --> 01:06:35.480
We should teach ourselves how to talk. Now go and talk to the sea,

01:06:35.560 --> 01:06:37.040
go and talk to some tree,

01:06:37.120 --> 01:06:40.640
go and talk to someone like that. Or best is to talk to me,

01:06:42.400 --> 01:06:47.120
to my photograph, so that's how you achieve

01:06:47.200 --> 01:06:50.400
a kind of control over your tongue.

01:06:50.640 --> 01:06:53.120
To talk sweetly.

01:06:53.200 --> 01:06:56.040
Some people have to go through penance for that.

01:06:56.120 --> 01:07:01.200
For them to talk sweetly is like

01:07:01.400 --> 01:07:03.960
taking rubab again.

01:07:04.320 --> 01:07:08.560
They just can't talk sweetly, just can't. Sarcasm.

01:07:08.640 --> 01:07:16.200
You see in that sarcasm, they have a special pleasure.

01:07:18.320 --> 01:07:20.400
Try to say something sweet.

01:07:20.480 --> 01:07:23.400
You can be humorous without being sarcastic.

01:07:23.560 --> 01:07:27.480
Humour is the best way. What is the need to be sarcastic?

01:07:27.960 --> 01:07:31.480
There's no need at all, it's a sign of cowardliness, I think, sarcasm.

01:07:31.640 --> 01:07:35.960
It is a sign that you want to hurt others, but you are not straight forward.

01:07:36.200 --> 01:07:39.200
So try to avoid sarcastic talking.

01:07:39.400 --> 01:07:43.800
If you are sarcastic, better tell your tongue to behave yourself.

01:07:44.640 --> 01:07:47.880
So a little disciplining towards yourself,

01:07:47.960 --> 01:07:53.040
punishment what you call, or the tapa - the penance has to work out.

01:07:53.720 --> 01:07:56.560
Now people have so many ways of

01:07:56.720 --> 01:07:59.960
seeing things. Some men want to see women all the time,

01:08:00.120 --> 01:08:02.400
some women want to see men all the time,

01:08:02.400 --> 01:08:04.880
or clothes, or anything, you see.

01:08:04.960 --> 01:08:07.200
Now, the difference is that

01:08:07.280 --> 01:08:10.400
when you see something, it reacts.

01:08:10.640 --> 01:08:13.800
The difference between my

01:08:13.880 --> 01:08:17.960
looking at any thing is that, that reacts.

01:08:21.880 --> 01:08:25.720
When I look at you, your Kundalini reacts, when I look at this,

01:08:25.960 --> 01:08:29.640
it gets vibrated. Kataksha, - Kataksha:

01:08:34.880 --> 01:08:39.400
Every glance; every glance

01:08:40.960 --> 01:08:46.720
makes the thing react and Nireekshana means, I know what it is.

01:08:46.880 --> 01:08:50.280
I know what it is. Just looking at a person I know what it is.

01:08:50.400 --> 01:08:54.280
Looking at a thing, I know what it is. - Nireekshana.

01:08:54.400 --> 01:08:56.720
But the whole thing is in the memory there, you see.

01:08:57.280 --> 01:09:00.800
Like we were going and they said we have only black stones.

01:09:00.880 --> 01:09:03.480
I said, "No, you have red also." He said, "Where? Do you know?"

01:09:03.640 --> 01:09:06.000
So I told them the exact spot where to get the red stones.

01:09:06.120 --> 01:09:07.440
He said, "How do you know, Mother?"

01:09:07.560 --> 01:09:08.960
I said, "We passed that way

01:09:09.120 --> 01:09:11.560
about eight years back and I know there are red stones."

01:09:11.720 --> 01:09:14.200
So everything I see

01:09:14.320 --> 01:09:18.800
gets vibrated and also I note

01:09:18.960 --> 01:09:23.400
what is there, and is all ready there

01:09:23.400 --> 01:09:26.560
to be used at the proper time.

01:09:27.720 --> 01:09:34.880
But what do I do? What do I do? I do nothing

01:09:37.400 --> 01:09:41.400
I do nothing. I don't think, I don't plan.

01:09:41.400 --> 01:09:44.400
Everything that you do, I don't do.

01:09:48.720 --> 01:09:55.640
So when you have that kind of a temperament you will be amazed!

01:09:57.400 --> 01:10:01.200
The amount of dynamism that will work it out.

01:10:01.280 --> 01:10:05.400
You don't have to create a dynamo, it is inside you.

01:10:05.400 --> 01:10:08.320
Let it work out.

01:10:08.720 --> 01:10:12.640
Today I had told Gavin that I won't have so much of a puja but I will talk.

01:10:13.200 --> 01:10:16.720
Because puja is alright, it talks for itself, and this thing.

01:10:17.200 --> 01:10:20.280
But I wanted to talk to you because now the time has come

01:10:20.400 --> 01:10:21.880
for us to go further.

01:10:22.400 --> 01:10:25.200
As a result of all this,

01:10:25.560 --> 01:10:29.760
all this and that what you do, you become the truth.

01:10:29.880 --> 01:10:32.520
You become the truth.

01:10:35.480 --> 01:10:38.800
So, in every chakra if you concentrate,

01:10:38.880 --> 01:10:44.480
and use the chakra to detach yourself from the particular

01:10:44.960 --> 01:10:47.320
quality of that chakra.

01:10:47.400 --> 01:10:52.400
Like, now for example, the Nabhi chakra does the digestion.

01:10:53.400 --> 01:10:58.720
Now you don't worry what you should eat to digest.

01:10:59.040 --> 01:11:00.960
Just detach yourself from there,

01:11:01.040 --> 01:11:05.320
with vibrations if you just see and eat; whatever is there,

01:11:05.480 --> 01:11:08.040
you will digest.

01:11:10.400 --> 01:11:15.400
And then you become the truth. Truth that is love, that is God.

01:11:16.480 --> 01:11:18.720
May God Bless you all.

